#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.58:0.2"
msgid "6. Abhisamayavagga "
msgstr "6. Comprehension "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: 58. Dutiyamahāsamuddasutta → dutiyasamuddasuttaṃ (bj) | samudda 2 (pts1)
msgctxt "sn56.58:0.3"
msgid "58. Dutiyamahāsamuddasutta "
msgstr "58. The Ocean (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
#. VAR: mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhayaṃ → mahāsamuddo parikkhayaṃ (bj, s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.1"
msgid "“Seyyathāpi, bhikkhave, mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhayaṃ pariyādānaṃ gaccheyya ṭhapetvā dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, suppose the water in the ocean dried up and evaporated except for two or three drops. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.2"
msgid "Taṃ kiṃ maññatha, bhikkhave, "
msgstr "What do you think, mendicants? "

msgctxt "sn56.58:1.3"
msgid "katamaṃ nu kho bahutaraṃ—yaṃ vā mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ, yāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti? "
msgstr "Which is more: the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, or the two or three drops left?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.4"
msgid "“Etadeva, bhante, bahutaraṃ mahāsamudde udakaṃ yadidaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ; appamattakāni dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhāni. "
msgstr "“Sir, the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated is certainly more. The two or three drops left are tiny. "

msgctxt "sn56.58:1.5"
msgid "Saṅkhampi na upenti, upanidhampi na upenti, kalabhāgampi na upenti mahāsamudde udakaṃ parikkhīṇaṃ pariyādinnaṃ upanidhāya dve vā tīṇi vā udakaphusitāni avasiṭṭhānī”ti. "
msgstr "Compared to the water in the ocean that has dried up and evaporated, it can’t be reckoned or compared, it’s not even a fraction.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.6"
msgid "“Evameva kho, bhikkhave, ariyasāvakassa … pe … "
msgstr "“In the same way, for a noble disciple … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.7"
msgid "yogo karaṇīyo”ti. "
msgstr "That’s why you should practice meditation …” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn56.58:1.8"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

